    "file": "packages/features/feature-opt-in/services/FeatureOptInService.ts",
    "line": 161,
    "severity": "high",
    "description": "Policy is hardcoded as 'permissive' instead of being read from feature configuration. This violates the established pattern where each OptInFeatureConfig has its own policy field. All features are forced to use the same policy regardless of their configured policy, ignoring the 'strict' policy option entirely.",
